@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam classBorderColor #F57F17
[*] --> Rejected
Rejected --> Closed : approve
Closed --> Pending : process
Pending --> Archived : approve
Archived --> Shipped : cancel
Archived : entry / log comment
Archived --> Rejected : revert
Shipped --> [*]
@enduml